sentence: Governor Ron DeSantis (R-FL) announced $125 million in funding for nursing and claimed the Florida government is going to take care of Disneys debt while speaking at Seminole State College, Sanford, Florida today.
title: Gov. DeSantis (R-FL) tells FL to not worry about Disneys debt: I have the biggest budget surplus weve ever had."
